content: No results matching your query could be found

comment.text: This translation key is used for the "EmptyFormGalleryScreenDescription" text, which appears on an empty form gallery screen as a message when no results match the user's query. It is likely displayed in a dialog or card component, indicating that no data was found. Translators should provide a concise and descriptive phrase to convey this message in other languages.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Aucun résultat correspondant à votre requête n'a pu être trouvé' is overly formal and complex for this context. A more natural and user-friendly translation would be preferred.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Aucun résultat trouvé correspondant à votre recherche

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Lao translation 'ບໍ່ພົບຜົນການຊອກຫາທີ່ກົງກັບຄຳຊອກຫາຂອງເຈົ້າ' is a literal translation and sounds somewhat unnatural in Lao. A more natural phrasing would be closer to 'ບໍ່ພົບຜົນການຄົ້ນຫາຕາມຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ເຈົ້າຊອກຫາ' or 'ບໍ່ພົບຜົນຕາມການຄົ້ນຫາຂອງທ່ານ'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ບໍ່ພົບຜົນຕາມການຄົ້ນຫາຂອງທ່ານ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Nu a putut fi găsit niciun rezultat care să corespundă interogării dvs' is a literal translation and sounds overly formal and awkward in Romanian. A more natural and user-friendly translation would be preferred.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Niciun rezultat nu a fost găsit pentru căutarea ta.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'ඔබගේ විමසුමට කිසිවක් නොගැළපේ' is a literal translation and while understandable, it lacks the natural flow of a user-facing message. A more appropriate translation would convey the same meaning in a more user-friendly way.
The word 'одговарају' is spelled correctly but could be improved for natural flow. While technically correct, it's a bit formal in this context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Нема резултата који одговара вашем упиту.
